title: Iranians Mark Anniversary of the 1979 U.S. Embassy Takeover and Call For a Gaza Ceasefire
description: Iranians gathered on the streets Saturday to mark the anniversary of the 1979 takeover of the U.S. Embassy in Tehran.

title: Israel’s Military and Hezbollah Exchange Fire Along Tense Lebanon-Israel Border
description: Israeli warplanes conducted airstrikes along the border with Lebanon Saturday as the militant Hezbollah group attacked Israeli army posts.

title: Nepal Rushes Rescue Operations After Strong Earthquake Kills at Least 157
description: Survivors of a strong earthquake that shook Nepal's northwest described sudden shaking followed by houses collapsing.

title: Ken Mattingly, Astronaut Who Helped Save Apollo 13 Crew, Dies at 87
description: “We lost one of our country’s heroes," NASA administrator Bill Nelson said in a statement.

title: Israeli Strikes Kill Multiple Civilians in Gaza Combat Zone, as Blinken Seeks More Aid
description: Israeli military strikes killed multiple civilians at a U.N. shelter and hospital in the main combat zone in the Gaza Strip.

title: The Biggest Myths About Motherhood in the Animal Kingdom
description: Maternal instinct is a long-standing myth that belittles the complexities of motherhood, writes Lucy Cooke.
